berni]] (778) \u2013 419 421 449 925\n*[[Port Coquitlam]] (778) \u2013 216 284 285 325 730 831 941\n*[[Port Moody]] (778) \u2013 217 272 355 522 731\n*[[Powell River, British Columbia|Powell River]] (778) \u2013 236\n*[[Prince George, British Columbia|Prince George]] (236) \u2013 331 423; (778) \u2013 281 349 415 416 497 510 675 693 763 764 890 983\n*[[Prince Rupert, British Columbia|Prince Rupert]] (778) \u2013 361 645\n*[[Quesnel, British Columbia|Quesnel]] (236) \u2013 424; (778) \u2013 334 414 466 768 920\n*[[Richmond, British Columbia|Richmond]] (236) \u2013 266; (778) \u2013 219 234 282 295 296 297 723 732 803 804 832 918 919 960\n*[[Radium Hot Springs, British Columbia|Radium Hot Springs]] (778) \u2013 527\n*[[Saanich, British Columbia|Saanich]] (778) \u2013 351 426 749 750\n*[[Smithers, British Columbia|Smithers]] (778) \u2013 210 640 648\n*[[Sooke, British Columbia|Sooke]] (778) \u2013 352 425\n*[[South Delta, British Columbia|South Delta]] (778) \u2013 263\n*[[Sparwood, British Columbia|Sparwood]] (778) \u2013 518\n*[[Surrey, British Columbia|Surrey]] is divided into the following local rate centres:\n**[[Cloverdale, Surrey|Cloverdale]] (778) \u2013 571 574 575 850\n**[[Newton, Surrey|Newton]] (236) \u2013 263; (778) \u2013 218 223 438 563 564 565 578 590 591 593 612 830 986\n**[[Whalley, Surrey|Whalley]] (778) \u2013 290 293 368 391 394 395 435 636 735 852\n**[[White Rock, British Columbia|White Rock]] (236) \u2013 265; (778) \u2013 291 292 294 390 545 736\n*[[Trail, British Columbia|Trail]] (778) \u2013 274 367 456 965\n*[[Vancouver]] (236) \u2013 317 520 521 777 826 828 888 984 985 986 987 988 989 990 991 992 993 994 995 996 997 998 999 (778) \u2013 200 222 224 227 228 229 230 231 232 233 235 239 288 300 302 309 316 317 318 319 320 321 322 323 327 328 329 330 331 333 370 371 372 373 374 375 377 378 379 381 383 446 452 504 532 554 558 580 588 600 628 668 680 681 682 683 684 686 689 706 707 708 710 712 713 714 724 737 782 783 785 786 788 800 807 819 828 8